id: pm-7sq6
title: "ADR: Test-coverage governance — 100% V8 thresholds with a curated include/exclude allowlist, a tests/unit file-count cap, and pure-logic extraction into small core modules"
description: "Test-coverage governance: 100% V8 thresholds with a curated include/exclude allowlist, a tests/unit file-count cap, and pure-logic extraction into small core modules"
type: Decision
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[6]: adr,architecture,"area:ci","area:tests",coverage,governance
